#

Sizzling Garlic Butter Steak Bites

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

DairySoy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

SteakQuick MealSavoryComfort Food

Description

Tender steak bites sautéed in a rich garlic butter sauce, served with a side of roasted vegetables.

Ingredients

  • Sirloin steak: 1 lb
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Rosemary: 1 tsp, fresh chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Bell peppers: 1 cup, assorted colors, diced
  • Zucchini: 1 cup, diced
  • Cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
